<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-inner">
    <h2 class="cta-title">
      <span class="zh">准备好优化您的全球覆盖范围了吗？</span>
      <span class="en">Ready to optimize your<br/>global reach?</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="cta-subtitle">
      <span class="zh">超过 18,000 家企业每天依赖义龙的精准服务。</span>
      <span class="en">Join 18,000+ businesses that rely on Yilong's kinetic precision every single day.</span>
    </p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/about_contact" class="btn btn-primary">
        <span class="zh">开始报价</span>
        <span class="en">Start Your Quote</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/about_contact" class="btn btn-secondary">
        <span class="zh">联系专家</span>
        <span class="en">Contact Our Experts</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9D5B00 0%, #C95E20 100%);
    padding: 72px 24px;
  }

  .cta-inner {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .cta-subtitle {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin: 0 0 36px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #fff;
    color: #9D5B00;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: #FFF1E2; }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: #fff;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
</style>
